  section.section-industries.section-content
    .container
      .card-wrap.-striped
        #health.card.card-expertise
          .card-body
            h2.card-title Health
            img.card-img(src=asset_url + "images/health.png", alt="Health-Logo")
            p.card-text Being an industry expert in creating solutions in healthcare sector, we help in transforming the healthcare delivery and service system. With more than a decadeâ€™s experience in making a difference in the healthcare industry, we provide ground-breaking solutions to the clients and help them empower the industry. With an innate focus to innovate and deliver quality and agile services, we have revolutionised us as valuable partners for entities in healthcare industry. The efforts have created new standards of excellence from an industry disruption point of view.
            .scroll-top
              a.btn-scroll(href='#industriesTop') go to top
        #media.card.card-expertise
          .card-body
            h2.card-title Media
            img.card-img(src=asset_url + 'images/media.png', alt='Media-Logo')
            p.card-text We help our clients by providing technical expertise for text, stills, and video cuts to suggest efficient marketing and advertising concepts. Since we are living in an era of data explosion, our team has an ability to process, slice and dice data to withdraw business intelligence and insights for further experience enhancement.
            .scroll-top
              a.btn-scroll(href='#industriesTop') go to top
        #insurance.card.card-expertise
          .card-body
            h2.card-title Insurance
            img.card-img(src=asset_url + 'images/insurance.png', alt='Insurance-Logo')
            p.card-text We help our customers in developing full-fledged platforms which are today integrated with various insurance companies, to offer instant quotations to the customers. Also, we have developed a complete MIS system for live tracking the sales pertinent to vehicle insurances. Backbone is the state of the art framework for issuing policies which includes features such as gamifications to boost the agency Point of Sale (PoS).
            .scroll-top
              a.btn-scroll(href='#industriesTop') go to top
        #sports.card.card-expertise
          .card-body
            h2.card-title Sports
            img.card-img(src=asset_url + 'images/sports.png', alt='Sports-Logo')
            p.card-text With a team of experts in developing solutions for sports sector, we have gathered enough expertise in developing technologies to enable this sector to disrupt and innovate tech solutions for offering revolutionary customer experience and sector transformation. We are geared up to take the journey ahead with newer and influential technologies such as AI, machine learning with predictive analysis, cloud infrastructure, IoT and big data.
            .scroll-top
              a.btn-scroll(href='#industriesTop') go to top
        #manufacturing.card.card-expertise
          .card-body
            h2.card-title Manufacturing
            img.card-img(src=asset_url + 'images/manufacturing.png', alt='Manufacturing-logo')
            p.card-text We help manufacturing companies and industries to identify efficiencies by applying the industry 4.0 principles and the industrial Internet of Things by transforming them into a more connected factory. Through our robust IoT framework, we thoroughly apply these methodologies to all the levels for improving the efficiency in the projects, which helps the companies to stand out from their competitors.
            .scroll-top
              a.btn-scroll(href='#industriesTop') go to top
        #education.card.card-expertise
          .card-body
            h2.card-title Education
            img.card-img(src=asset_url + 'images/education.png', alt='Education-Logo')
            p.card-text In the field of education, we develop best of services through new-age tech platforms as the demand is higher than ever. Also, we help companies which focus on education and learnings with AI-led solutions to maximize productivity, simultaneously saving time and resources in their businesses.
