            h2.card-title Tourisum
            img.card-img(src=asset_url + 'images/tourisum.png', alt='Tourisum-Logo')
            p.card-text At Josh Software, we are already ahead of the curve in terms of providing that technological edge to this sector. With a team of experts in developing solutions for tourism sector. AI, machine learning with predictive analysis, cloud infrastructure, IoT and big data are going to influence this sector even more than we could ever imagine. In the past one decade, we have gathered deep expertise and have already started using these technologies to enable this sector to disrupt and innovate for revolutionalizing customer experience and sector transformation.
